    { intros s t hst,
      rw subtype.ext_iff at *,
      exact closure_eq_of_is_open s.2 t.2 hst },
    { rintros ⟨t, h1⟩,
      use ⟨t, hO.symm ▸ h1⟩,
      ext s,
      simpa using closure_eq_iff_is_closed.mpr (hC ▸ h1) } 
  end⟩
`

refine ⟨λ (s : ↥O), ⟨closure s.val, is_closed_closure⟩, _⟩, 
begin 
  refine ⟨_, _⟩,
  { intros s₁ s₂ h_eq, 
    apply subtype.eq, 
    rwa [closure_eq_of_is_open s₁.2 s₂.2] at h_eq },
  { rintros ⟨t, h_tt⟩,
    rcases hC.symm ▸ h_tt with h_t_open,
    use ⟨t, by rwa ←hO⟩,
    rw subtype.ext_iff_val,
    exact closure_eq_of_is_closed h_t_open }
end
